#: src/uagent/checks.py:20
msgid ""
"Please install Git. Example: sudo apt install git (Ubuntu/Debian) or sudo"
" yum install git (CentOS/RHEL)"
msgstr ""
"Git суулгана уу. Жишээ нь: sudo apt install git (Ubuntu/Debian) эсвэл "
"sudo yum install git (CentOS/RHEL)"

#: src/uagent/checks.py:23
msgid ""
"Please install Git. If using Homebrew: brew install git, or install Xcode"
" Command Line Tools: xcode-select --install"
msgstr ""
"Git суулгана уу. Хэрэв Homebrew ашиглаж байгаа бол: brew install git, "
"эсвэл Xcode Command Line Tools: xcode-select --install суулгана уу."

